# Frontend Component Organization

- Extract components to `frontend/src/core/components/` when:
  - Used in more than one place, OR
  - Used so frequently that consistency is important (e.g., Button, filters, EmailChipInput)
- Prefer using existing core components over bespoke new components

## Styled Components

- Use `.wrrappers.ts` files for styled-components (e.g., `Button.wrappers.ts`)
- Use theme colors and values, never bespoke colors

```typescript
// ❌ BAD - bespoke color
const Container = styled.div`
  background: #f5f5f5;
`;

// ✅ GOOD - theme color
const Container = styled.div`
  background: ${({ theme }) => theme.colors.background};
`;
```
